languages.text: "Я расформировал его сеть соглядатаев, а самого его отослал выслеживать более легкую цель. Полагаю, он с головой ушел в работу, пытаясь загладить свою вину — неудивительно, что он не показывается без результата".

"I disbanded his network of spies and sent Achilleas himself off to track down an easier target. I imagine he has buried himself in his task, trying to make amends. He will be reluctant to show up empty-handed, so it is no surprise we have not yet seen him."

languages.text: “我解散了他的线人网络，派阿吉里亚斯亲自去追踪某个更容易追查的目标。我猜他应该是在埋头工作，打算弥补过错。他肯定不打算空手而归，因此我们最近没见到他，也不足为奇。”
languages.original_text: "I disbanded his network of spies and sent Achilleas himself off to track down an easier target. I imagine he has buried himself in his task, trying to make amends. He will be reluctant to show up empty-handed, so it is no surprise we have not yet seen him."

traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: « J'ai démantelé son réseau d'espions et l'ai envoyé traquer une cible un peu plus à sa portée. J'imagine qu'il se consacre entièrement à cette nouvelle tâche pour essayer de se racheter et qu'il n'osera pas se présenter les mains vides, d'où son absence prolongée. »
languages.original_text: "I disbanded his network of spies and sent Achilleas himself off to track down an easier target. I imagine he has buried himself in his task, trying to make amends. He will be reluctant to show up empty-handed, so it is no surprise we have not yet seen him."

traits.speaker: HeinrixCompanion

languages.text: «Disolví su red de espías y envié al propio Achilleas a rastrear un objetivo más sencillo. Imagino que se ha sumido en su tarea, intentando compensar sus faltas. Como no querrá aparecer con las manos vacías, no me sorprende que no le hayamos visto».

languages.text: 「奴の諜報網は解散し、アキレアス本人は簡単に御せるターゲットの追跡に出した。任務にのめり込んでいるのだろう、償いというわけだ。何の手柄もなく現れるつもりはないはずだ、しばらく姿を見ないのも当然というもの」
languages.original_text: "I disbanded his network of spies and sent Achilleas himself off to track down an easier target. I imagine he has buried himself in his task, trying to make amends. He will be reluctant to show up empty-handed, so it is no surprise we have not yet seen him."

languages.text: "Ich habe sein Spionagenetzwerk aufgelöst und Achilleas selbst auf ein leichteres Ziel angesetzt. Ich vermute, dass er sich in diese Aufgabe verbissen hat, um Buße zu tun. Er wird nicht mit leeren Händen zurückkehren wollen, daher ist es nicht überraschend, dass wir ihn noch nicht gesehen haben."

languages.text: "Casus şebekesini dağıtıp Achilleas'ı da daha kolay bir avın peşine yolladım. Hatasını telafi etmek için görevine gömülmüştür diye düşünüyorum. Eli boş dönmek istemiyordur, bu yüzden onu görmemiş olmamız şaşırtıcı değil."
